  "description": "GalactiWar is a full-blown galactic history simulator. Empires will emerge, grow populations, conquer territory, deal with rebellions, form alliances, advance in technology, and eventually fall. Storylines emerge as empires rise and fall over the centuries. You may choose to observe the simulation or intervene with godly powers.\n\nFeatures• Economy simulation\n\n• Emergent stories\n\n• Huge space battles\n\n• Diplomacy\n\n• Detailed statistics\n\n• Technology levels\n\n• Buildings\n\n• Trading\n\n• Characters (Leaders, Governors, and Captains)\n\n• Destructive or helpful god powers\n\n• Frigate, Destroyer, Cruiser, Carrier, and Dreadnought spaceships\n\n• Random events\n\n• Population and cultures\n\n• Pirates\n\n• Doomsday weapons\n\n• Crises",
  "description_short": "Watch empires rise and fall, or intervene with godly powers, in GalactiWar, a space empire simulation sandbox game.",
